<item>
            <title>[DATAREST-473] Add option to disable default exposure of public repository interfaces</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/DATAREST-473</link>
                <project id="10901" key="DATAREST">Spring Data REST</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If Spring Data repositories are used in library projects, preventing them from being exposed (i.e. annotating them with &lt;tt&gt;@RepositoryRestResource(exported = false&lt;/tt&gt;) might not be possible.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We should introduce a dedicated configuration option to configure the default exposure for public repository interfaces.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="62109">DATAREST-473</key>
            <summary>Add option to disable default exposure of public repository interfaces</summary>
